{"tid":202767,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"一個尼馬=兩個普巴 留名睇曼聯再破世界紀錄","createTime":"2017-04-15T17:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T03:13:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"095014b90e0274a80f02bf09fe86ec8f6625562e","tid":202767,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"西班牙《Sport》報道，英超曼聯已經準備好開水喉，斥資兩億歐元、即係大約16.8億港紙，喺西甲嘅巴塞隆拿引入巴西前鋒尼馬。<br />\n<br />\n報道話，兩億歐元呢個價錢，係巴西國家隊隊長尼馬喺巴塞嘅贖身費，如果真係呢個價嘅話，將會輕鬆打破本來已經由紅魔鬼打破嘅轉會費紀錄。依家嘅紀錄，就係曼聯舊年夏天以一億歐元，喺祖雲達斯簽保羅普巴返嚟果陣，亦即係話，一個尼馬嘅身價，足足等於兩個「舞王」普巴。<br />\n除咗呢個癲價轉會費之外，報道亦都話曼聯打算令尼馬成為全世界人工最高嘅球員，周薪將會超過415,000鎊（約405萬港元）。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170327/large/1490604455_21e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170327%2Flarge%2F1490604455_21e0.jpg&h=14ef5a0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ff990295187934888409fb3da7cf87c11685e5c","tid":202767,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"再嘈買埋你個蘇亞雷斯<br />\n等你冇得吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25294ae401d639f2645d6f113c2f5aea0501cfe6","tid":202767,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T17:47:18.000Z","msg":"曼聯抬價部開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時到降價部開工 將普巴賤賣出去九流聯賽"},{"pid":"ccce80577e66024669e83e2d65008f9fb8dafc4a","tid":202767,"uid":31048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T00:49:20.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"52fe3acc786632d4d2e8fc7a655b0708d1ec264b","tid":202767,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T00:54:33.000Z","msg":"好少錢啫，賣C朗果筆錢都未用完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc2460d70b4ecc078128c11939c8530ae956d4a","tid":202767,"uid":106450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201